---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Chouhan Industries | Open Source Hardware"
  description="Precision hardware, designed for the public and published in full. Schematics, tolerances, and processes, without restriction."
  url="https://chouhan.ai"
  home
>

  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Open Hardware · Est. 2025</p>
      <h1>Open by Design.<br><em>Built to Last.</em></h1>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">Precision hardware, designed for the public and published in full: schematics, tolerances,
        and processes, without restriction.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M4 7L10 13L16 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p class="manifesto-text">
          Chouhan Industries was founded on a single conviction: that the best hardware should be free for
          anyone to study, build upon, and improve. We manufacture to the highest standard and publish
          everything: schematics, processes, and tolerances, without restriction.
        </p>
        <img src="logos/oshw-logo-800-px.webp" alt="Open Source Hardware" class="oshw-badge">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="capabilities">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-label">Capabilities</p>
      <div class="capabilities-grid">
        <div class="capability-item">
          <span class="cap-number">01</span>
          <div class="cap-rule"></div>
          <h3>Open Source</h3>
          <p>Every schematic, tolerance spec, and process document is public record. No proprietary lock-in.
            No licensing walls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="capability-item">
          <span class="cap-number">02</span>
          <div class="cap-rule"></div>
          <h3>Manufacturing</h3>
          <p>Full-stack production across mechanical, electronic, and systems hardware. Every step owned
            in-house.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="capability-item">
          <span class="cap-number">03</span>
          <div class="cap-rule"></div>
          <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
          <p>Testing is not a phase. It is the process. Every unit meets the same standard, without exception.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="philosophy">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-label">Philosophy</p>
      <h2 class="philosophy-statement">
        Hardware is<br>too important<br>to be kept<br><em>closed.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
